---
import { ChevronDown } from '@lucide/astro';
---

<section class="hero-section" data-hero="true">
 <div class="hero-content">
 <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; margin-bottom:16px;">
 <div style="width:28px; height:2px; background:#2db832; flex-shrink:0;"></div>
      <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#2db832;">South King County, WA · Licensed & Insured</span>
 </div>

 <h1 style="
 font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;
 font-size: clamp(44px, 6vw, 72px);
 line-height: 1.0;
 color: #ffffff;
 letter-spacing: 0.02em;
 margin: 0 0 16px 0;
 ">
      Concrete, Excavation<br>&amp; Site Work<br>in South King County, WA
 </h1>

 <p style="
 font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
 font-size: 15px;
 color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
 line-height: 1.65;
 max-width: 480px;
 margin: 0 0 28px 0;
 ">
 Driveways, patios, retaining walls, foundations, slabs, demo, and excavation from a local contractor built to licensed & insured standards.
 </p>

 <div class="hero-ctas">
 <a href="/contact" class="hero-cta hero-cta-primary">Request a Free Estimate</a>
 <a href="tel:+12535550182" class="hero-cta hero-cta-secondary">Call (253) 555-0182</a>
 </div>
 </div>

 <a href="#trust-bar" class="scroll-arrow" aria-label="Scroll down">
 <ChevronDown size={28} color="white" />
 </a>
</section>

<style>
 .hero-section {
 position: relative;
 width: 100%;
 /* Fill exactly the viewport below the nav — not 100vh + nav */
 height: calc(100svh - 56px);
 min-height: 480px;
 background-image:
 linear-gradient(to right, rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.92) 0%, rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.65) 55%, rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.2) 100%),
 url('/images/mac_working_01.jpg');
 background-size: cover;
 background-position: center center;
 display: flex;
 align-items: flex-end;
 overflow: visible;
 box-sizing: border-box;
 }

 @media (min-width: 768px) {
 .hero-section {
 height: calc(100svh - 68px);
 }
 }

 .hero-content {
 position: relative;
 z-index: 2;
 padding: 0 24px 52px;
 max-width: 700px;
 width: 100%;
 }

 @media (min-width: 768px) {
 .hero-content {
 padding: 0 64px 56px;
 }
 }

 .scroll-arrow {
 position: absolute;
 bottom: 18px;
 left: 50%;
 transform: translateX(-50%);
 color: white;
 opacity: 0.6;
 display: flex;
 align-items: center;
 justify-content: center;
 z-index: 10;
 animation: chevron-bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
 }

 @keyframes chevron-bounce {
 0%, 100% {
 transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0px);
 }
 50% {
 transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(10px);
 }
 }

 .hero-ctas {
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: row;
 flex-wrap: nowrap;
 gap: 10px;
 }

 .hero-cta {
 flex: 1;
 min-width: 0;
 font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
 font-size: 11px;
 font-weight: 700;
 letter-spacing: 0.06em;
 text-transform: uppercase;
 padding: 12px 10px;
 border-radius: 2px;
 text-decoration: none;
 text-align: center;
 display: block;
 }

 .hero-cta-primary {
 background: #2db832;
 color: #ffffff;
 }

 .hero-cta-secondary {
 background: transparent;
 color: #ffffff;
 border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
 }

 @media (min-width: 768px) {
 .hero-ctas {
 gap: 12px;
 }

 .hero-cta {
 flex: none;
 font-size: 13px;
 letter-spacing: 0.08em;
 padding: 13px 24px;
 }

 .hero-cta-secondary {
 padding: 12px 24px;
 }
 }
</style>
